data.description: Step into your dream home and experience the charm of country living in this meticulously remodeled CBS Traditional ranch-style residence, boasting 2,900 square feet of living space nestled on just under an acre of land adorned with majestic mature oak trees and a delightful tire swing. Transporting you to a bygone era, this warm and inviting abode offers a glimpse into the past while seamlessly integrating modern amenities and contemporary design. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this home has undergone a stunning transformation with meticulous attention to detail. Step into the heart of the home and discover a new chef's paradise in the massive open dream kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances, exquisite wood cabinets, and breathtaking granite countertops. (See More Remarks) The expansive island with a farmer's sink provides ample seating and storage, while a dedicated coffee drink bar station with a wine cooler adds a touch of luxury. Crafted barn doors open to reveal a pantry storage adorned with programmable accent lighting, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The newly renovated primary bathroom offers a personal oasis with a spacious shower featuring dual shower heads and controls, along with comfortable benches for added convenience. A new vanity and commode complete the space, offering ample room for personalization. The generously sized primary bedroom suite boasts a large walk-in closet, providing ample storage and comfort. Entertain with ease in the main living and dining area, adorned with soft colors and new tile flooring throughout. Two additional bedrooms offer versatility, ideal for an office or mother-in-law suite, while the back family room opens to a spacious country backyard featuring a pole barn, above-ground pool, and a cozy firepit area. Additional features include a 2020 new metal roof, HVAC, and water heater, ensuring comfort and efficiency year-round. A laundry room equipped with a washer, dryer, and sink adds convenience, while a bonus additional space offers endless possibilities. The former garage area has been converted into over 540 square feet of flexible space, ideal for a family room, playroom, home gym, office, or hobbyist's retreat. Situated in the serene countryside yet conveniently located near the City of Okeechobee, residents can enjoy easy access to medical facilities, shopping, dining, and year-round events, festivals, rodeos, and holiday parades. Don't miss the opportunity to make this idyllic retreat your forever home. Schedule your showing today and experience the epitome of country living with modern flair.
